      <title>Biden set an ambitious new climate goal. Will it still matter under Trump?</title>
      <author>Jeff Brady</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/12/19/nx-s1-5233131/biden-climate-trump</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2024/12/19/nx-s1-5233131/biden-climate-trump</comments>
